<p>
  JavaScript uses the same familiar operators as most other modern languages. Below are some of the most common
  operators.
</p>

<pre>
+ // Addition
- // Subtraction
* // Multiplication
/ // Division
= // Assignment</pre>

<p>
  Simply typing in an expression to the browser console will return the answer.
</p>

